VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT \.setSeed\s*\(
WHEN EXPR PRESENT:setSeed.*currentTimeMillis|setSeed.*nanoTime|setSeed.*System\.current|setSeed.*hashCode
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects SecureRandom seeded with a timestamp or other predictable value, destroying cryptographic randomness.
TRACE Externalized mobile rule logic for SecureRandom Seeded with Predictable Timestamp.
